extends baseEmail

block content
  p(style="font-size:16px; color:#333;")
    | We received a request to verify your identity for Terramartz. Please use the OTP below to proceed:

  //- OTP Block
  div(style="margin:20px 0; text-align:center;")
    h3(style="display:inline-block; background-color:#007bff; color:#fff; padding:12px 24px; border-radius:6px; font-family:Arial, sans-serif; font-weight:bold; font-size:24px;")
